\nsuggest that ZnV$_{2}$O$_{4}$ compound can be a good thermoelectric material in\nhigh temperature range.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 4 May 2016 20:46:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 9 Sep 2016 09:42:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-30"}
